CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, Philadelphia edition, May 11, 1940, pg. 15 reads: "A.M.E.'s Open General Conference In Detroit - No. 1 - Bishops Fountain and Sims, conratulate Dr. W.R. Wilkes on his assignment to deliver the fraternal address to the A.M.E. Zion conference at Washington, D.C."
TitMainTitle: Bishop Fountain and Bishop Sims congratulating Dr. W. R. Wilkes in Ebenezer AME Church during AME General Conference, Detroit
